<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,1891,2026]" pageId="2" pageNumber="592">
The unique male holotype of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Obenberger" authorityYear="1944" box="[484,592,1892,1915]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Melanophila" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="592" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="caseyi">
